{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-works-work-js","path":"/auction-house/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Leonardo Melo"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bd3347c1-488d-5c09-89fc-1209db07eb82","excerpt":"Introduction Acquire.ly is a online auction website with support for realtime bidding, built with Spring MVC and hosted in AWS ECâ€¦","rawMarkdownBody":"\r\n# Introduction\r\n\r\nAcquire.ly is a online auction website with support for realtime bidding, built with Spring MVC and hosted in AWS EC2. \r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\nThe authentication and registration was implemented manually, without external APIs.\r\n\r\n![sign-up](/imgs/sign-up.png)\r\n\r\nAfter authentication that user is prompted to the home page where all the ads are displayed, which can be filtered by categories and ordered by price.\r\n\r\n![product](/imgs/product-page.png)\r\n\r\nTo user also has the option to add products by specifying the product details as shown in the following figure.\r\n\r\n![add-product](/imgs/add-product.png)\r\n\r\nPrice information can be tracked in realtime through WebSockets. The client initiates a connection to the server indicating the listings he is interested in (information which is stored in the cookies), and a connection is created which keeps sending information until it is closed, which removes the need for long-polling applications.\r\n\r\n![realtime](/imgs/realtime-auctions.png)\r\n\r\nIt is also possible to see product pages, which include details about the product such descriptions, images, videos and even music. \r\n\r\n![product](/imgs/product-page-simple.png)\r\n\r\nThe application has includes a back office section where an admin can manage listings, with the following functionalities available:\r\n\r\n- Alter user roles\r\n- Delete user accounts\r\n- Add new options for auctions (e.g., new auction durations)\r\n- Add new categories\r\n- Verify user accounts\r\n\r\n![backoffice](/imgs/backoffice.png)\r\n","html":"<h1>Introduction</h1>\n<p>Acquire.ly is a online auction website with support for realtime bidding, built with Spring MVC and hosted in AWS EC2. </p>\n<h1>Implementation</h1>\n<p>The authentication and registration was implemented manually, without external APIs.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/29007/sign-up.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.05405405405405%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sign-up\"\n        title=\"sign-up\"\n        src=\"/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/fcda8/sign-up.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/12f09/sign-up.png 148w,\n/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/e4a3f/sign-up.png 295w,\n/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/fcda8/sign-up.png 590w,\n/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/efc66/sign-up.png 885w,\n/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/c83ae/sign-up.png 1180w,\n/static/6802843e1c28d54f28749de3a793eecf/29007/sign-up.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>After authentication that user is prompted to the home page where all the ads are displayed, which can be filtered by categories and ordered by price.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/bf286/product-page.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.64864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"product\"\n        title=\"product\"\n        src=\"/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/fcda8/product-page.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/12f09/product-page.png 148w,\n/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/e4a3f/product-page.png 295w,\n/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/fcda8/product-page.png 590w,\n/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/efc66/product-page.png 885w,\n/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/c83ae/product-page.png 1180w,\n/static/090016729cae1ff742dfa786e81cae6b/bf286/product-page.png 1688w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To user also has the option to add products by specifying the product details as shown in the following figure.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/cc7de/add-product.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add-product\"\n        title=\"add-product\"\n        src=\"/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/fcda8/add-product.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/12f09/add-product.png 148w,\n/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/e4a3f/add-product.png 295w,\n/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/fcda8/add-product.png 590w,\n/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/efc66/add-product.png 885w,\n/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/c83ae/add-product.png 1180w,\n/static/66ff7e9e9634a94ce295c3506f03d52f/cc7de/add-product.png 1605w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Price information can be tracked in realtime through WebSockets. The client initiates a connection to the server indicating the listings he is interested in (information which is stored in the cookies), and a connection is created which keeps sending information until it is closed, which removes the need for long-polling applications.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/fd8a5/realtime-auctions.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"realtime\"\n        title=\"realtime\"\n        src=\"/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/fcda8/realtime-auctions.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/12f09/realtime-auctions.png 148w,\n/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/e4a3f/realtime-auctions.png 295w,\n/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/fcda8/realtime-auctions.png 590w,\n/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/efc66/realtime-auctions.png 885w,\n/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/c83ae/realtime-auctions.png 1180w,\n/static/aa4473083a3b96f763246440087ac606/fd8a5/realtime-auctions.png 1659w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>It is also possible to see product pages, which include details about the product such descriptions, images, videos and even music. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/6aacb/product-page-simple.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.567567567567565%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"product\"\n        title=\"product\"\n        src=\"/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/fcda8/product-page-simple.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/12f09/product-page-simple.png 148w,\n/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/e4a3f/product-page-simple.png 295w,\n/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/fcda8/product-page-simple.png 590w,\n/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/efc66/product-page-simple.png 885w,\n/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/c83ae/product-page-simple.png 1180w,\n/static/b7ad14685e6e014348ef225513f305c6/6aacb/product-page-simple.png 1347w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The application has includes a back office section where an admin can manage listings, with the following functionalities available:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Alter user roles</li>\n<li>Delete user accounts</li>\n<li>Add new options for auctions (e.g., new auction durations)</li>\n<li>Add new categories</li>\n<li>Verify user accounts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/6f92b/backoffice.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"backoffice\"\n        title=\"backoffice\"\n        src=\"/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/fcda8/backoffice.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/12f09/backoffice.png 148w,\n/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/e4a3f/backoffice.png 295w,\n/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/fcda8/backoffice.png 590w,\n/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/efc66/backoffice.png 885w,\n/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/c83ae/backoffice.png 1180w,\n/static/5206a72093e1646fe1be505a97c2c691/6f92b/backoffice.png 1501w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Acquirely","date":"November 20, 2018","description":"Auction website with real time transactions through the use of websockets.","time":null,"stack":["Java Server Pages","Spring MVC","AWS EC2","WebSocket"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/auction-house/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}